---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | Stone Dragon Media"
  description="Read the Stone Dragon Media privacy policy to understand how we collect, use, and protect your personal information."
  canonical="https://stonedragonmedia.com/privacy-policy/"
  ogUrl="https://stonedragonmedia.com/privacy-policy/"
  robots="noindex, follow"
>
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <style>
      :root {
        --surface: rgba(243, 248, 253, 0.95);
      }

      .wrapper {
        max-width: 980px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 2rem clamp(1.1rem, 2.5vw, 2.4rem) 3rem;
      }

      .card {
        background: var(--surface);
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 1rem;
        padding: 1.4rem;
        box-shadow: 0 16px 30px rgba(18, 45, 69, 0.12);
      }

      h1,
      h2 {
        font-family: "Sora", sans-serif;
        color: var(--brand-strong);
      }

      p,
      li {
        color: var(--ink-soft);
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      a {
        color: var(--brand-strong);
      }
    </style>
  </Fragment>

  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="card">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p><em>Effective date: May 19, 2026</em></p>
      <p>
        Stone Dragon Media (&ldquo;we&rdquo;, &ldquo;us&rdquo;, or &ldquo;our&rdquo;) operates
        stonedragonmedia.com. This policy explains what information we collect, how we use it,
        and who we share it with.
      </p>

      <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
      <p><strong>Information you provide</strong> — When you submit our contact form we collect:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Your name and email address</li>
        <li>Company name and project timeline (optional)</li>
        <li>Project details you choose to share</li>
      </ul>
      <p><strong>Information collected automatically</strong> — When you visit our site we collect standard web analytics data through Google Analytics, including pages visited, time on site, approximate geographic location (country/region), browser type, and device type. This data is associated with a randomly assigned identifier, not your name or email.</p>

      <h2>Cookies</h2>
      <p>
        Our site uses cookies set by Google Analytics to distinguish visitors and aggregate usage
        statistics, and by hCaptcha to verify that contact form submissions are not automated.
        These cookies are set by third parties under their own privacy policies (see below). No
        cookies are used for advertising or cross-site tracking by Stone Dragon Media.
      </p>

      <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>We use the following services to operate this site. Each processes data under its own privacy policy:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Google Analytics (Google LLC)</strong> — measures site usage and performance.
          Data is processed under Google&rsquo;s privacy terms at
          <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">policies.google.com/privacy</a>.
          You can opt out via <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google&rsquo;s opt-out browser add-on</a>.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Web3Forms</strong> — receives and routes contact form submissions to us by email.
          Form data is transmitted securely and is not retained by Web3Forms beyond delivery.
          See <a href="https://web3forms.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">web3forms.com/privacy</a>.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>hCaptcha (Intuition Machines, Inc.)</strong> — protects our contact form from
          automated submissions. hCaptcha may collect interaction data for CAPTCHA verification.
          See <a href="https://www.hcaptcha.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">hcaptcha.com/privacy</a>.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Cloudflare</strong> — provides CDN, DDoS protection, and DNS services. Cloudflare
          may process request metadata (IP address, headers) in transit.
          See <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">cloudflare.com/privacypolicy</a>.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Responding to your inquiry and discussing your project</li>
        <li>Delivering agreed services and communicating project updates</li>
        <li>Understanding how our site is used so we can improve it</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We do not sell your personal information. We do not share it with third parties except the service providers listed above, or as required by law.</p>

      <h2>Data Retention</h2>
      <p>
        Contact form submissions are retained in email for as long as the client relationship is
        active and for a reasonable period afterward for business records. Google Analytics data
        is retained for 14 months under our account settings, after which it is automatically
        deleted.
      </p>

      <h2>Your Choices</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>You may request access to, correction of, or deletion of personal information you have provided by contacting us.</li>
        <li>You may opt out of Google Analytics data collection using the <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Analytics Opt-out Browser Add-on</a>.</li>
        <li>Most browsers allow you to block or delete cookies through their settings.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>
        We may update this policy as our site evolves. The effective date at the top of this page
        will reflect the most recent revision.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Privacy questions or data requests can be submitted through our
        <a href="/contact">contact form</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
